OL,3,CScottish trade union confirms that
OL,4,Cstrikes will not take place this week
OL,6,FThe ballot is set to open on 15 August
OL,7,Fand will close on 5 September.
OL,9,FGraham McNab, Unite's lead negotiator
OL,10,Ffor local government said: "Unite
OL,11,Fmembers across all of Scotland's
OL,12,Fcouncils should be applauded for
OL,13,Fstanding firm. They have remained
OL,14,Fresolute in an effort to secure a
OL,15,Ffairer and better pay offer.
OL,17,F"We believe that the new pay offer is
OL,18,Fcredible. For the first time in years,
OL,19,Fit will mean all council workers
OL,20,Freceiving an above inflation increase.
